eventDecorators.name: AddNewPermittedAddress
eventDecorators.description: Event emitted when a supply is withdrawn. Emitted when token is purchased by `to` in `token` for `price`.

eventDecorators.name: OwnershipTransferred
eventDecorators.description: Event emitted when a supply is withdrawn. Emitted when token is purchased by `to` in `token` for `price`.

eventDecorators.name: RemovePermittedAddress
eventDecorators.description: Event emitted when a supply is withdrawn. Emitted when token is purchased by `to` in `token` for `price`.

functionDecorators.name: addNewAddress
functionDecorators.description: adding a new address to permittedAddresses.

functionDecorators.name: disableAddress
functionDecorators.description: Disables an address, meaning SmartFunds will no longer be able to connect to them if they're not already connected.

functionDecorators.name: isMatchTypes
functionDecorators.description: check if input address has the same type as addressType.

functionDecorators.name: owner
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address of the current owner.

functionDecorators.name: renounceOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

functionDecorators.name: transferOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

functionDecorators.name: updateAddressType
functionDecorators.description: update address type as owner for case if wrong address type was set.
